commit.message: Add pwndbg-gui to Projects list
Prepare for work on the next release
Bump version to 0.11.0.0 for release
Document how to make a release
Move a comment in .flake8 on its own line to avoid an error from flake

Use shutil.which instead of distutils.spawn.find_executable

distutils.spawn.find_executable is deprecated and is going to be removed
in Python 3.12.
Run pyupgrade on the whole codebase
Add a test for example.py
Add the UDB time-travel debugger to the list of projects using pygdbmi
Run mypy in a stricter configuration and address missing types
Update Python examples in `README.md` (#69)
Convert unittest-based tests to pytest
Exclude some backup, cache, etc. files from the manifest

Wait for the GDB process to exit in GdbController.exit

This fixes a crash on Windows.

Original patch by matkuki (https://github.com/cs01/pygdbmi/pull/68),
modified by Marco Barisione.
Use the new `format` session to re-format imports
Use `isort` in the `format` and `lint` sessions
Add a `format` session for `nox` to format source files
add similar projects to readme (#74)
